title: Stata 13 - Win&Mac, small/IC/SE/MP, full install
description:
full installation - both win (32/64) and osx versions

two license files - one for the small/IC version, the other one for the SE/MP-8 version - pick the one you want and uncompress it

on win machines, the uncompressed license file stata.lic goes in Stata's root folder (where the stata executable resides)
on osx machine, it should go in either "/usr/local/stata" or "/Applications/Stata/" (can't check, don't have a mac)

as of now, both licenses allow online updating - if they get blocked by stata corp, just use the manual update method (google it!)

if you don't know how to install/set up stata following these simple rules, please do everyone a favor and buy it
